parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in an accident
driver side knee airbag caused hematoma and second-degree burn
airbag light came on and off
airbag recall was replaced but airbags did not deploy in a subsequent accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall remedy parts can lead to a delay in the repair of the vehicle, putting the driver and passengers at risk of serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Parts to repair the recall were unavailable
dealer could not acquire a replacement airbag
manufacturer exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
parts were on backorder
dealer stated that the remedy parts would not be available until a later date.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Poor communication and service from dealerships and manufacturers can lead to frustration and a delay in the repair of the vehicle, putting the driver and passengers at risk of serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Dealer refused to schedule an appointment
dealer was unresponsive
manufacturer exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
dealer could not verify when the parts would be supplied
manufacturer was not made aware of the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety hazards, including the inability to lock doors, malfunctioning of the horn, and electrical fires.
symptoms: Doors not locking or unlocking
horn not working
smoke or fire emanating from the passenger seat
dashboard vinyl melting
and warning lights illuminating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock system can cause safety hazards, including the inability to lock doors, which can lead to unauthorized entry or exit.
symptoms: Doors not locking or unlocking
no click heard when trying to lock doors
and doors unlocking electronically when manually locked from inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbags deploying unexpectedly
multiple airbags deploying at once
and injuries sustained from airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause loss of control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Horn not working
and steering wheel clock spring failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting and distortion of the dashboard can cause a glare on the windshield, obstructing the driver's view and potentially leading to accidents. Additionally, the sticky surface can be a distraction and discomfort for the driver.
symptoms: The dashboard appears melted
warped
or distorted
causing a glare on the windshield
the dashboard feels sticky or tacky to the touch
the instrument panel is affected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuators can compromise the security and safety of the vehicle, making it vulnerable to theft or unauthorized access.
symptoms: The doors fail to lock
the doors fail to unlock
the door locks are inoperable
there are no warning indicators illuminated.
